SUMMARY:Scott Manley Hadley: Bald Personality Disorder
LOCATION:London
DESCRIPTION:No hair. No worries. Well\, some worries... Alternative comedy 
 show on mental health\, hair loss\, gender\, money and parenting. Includes 
 sequins\, thighs\, an interactive bald-themed quiz\, poetry\, costumes\, or
 iginal music. Scott Manley Hadley\, AKA SOLID BALD\, is a poet turned comed
 ian who has been Highly Commended in the Forward Prizes for Poetry and whos
 e blog\, TriumphOfTheNow.com\, has been quoted in the New Yorker. Scott has
  appeared as a talking head discussing hair loss on BBC Three. Leicester Sq
 uare Theatre New Act of the Year 2025 semi-finalist. Bald but not forgotten
 .\nMore info: https://comedyatlas.app/comedy-atlas/event/scott-manley-hadle
 y-bald-personality-disorder-5798/
